metadata.description:
Owning this NFT grants you the following title in the AF realms:

"NEO Witness"

World notice: Unusual activity was reported in sectors NEO-4 to NEO-7. All players are advised to avoid affected areas. If in immediate danger automatically log off. Please be aware that The Grid is one of the strangest occurrences in Axyz and its contamination spreads fast. A team of Netrunners is investigating and working on securing the area and removing the contamination.
metadata.name: CONTAMINATED
